					<description><![CDATA[The most important step is to make the time to write each day. If you make the time, you&#039;ll write more. You need to decide what&#039;s most important to you. If writing is one of those things, you will find time no matter how busy you are. If you don&#039;t, writing isn&#039;t important to you.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The most important step is to make the time to write each day. If you make the time, you&#8217;ll write more. You need to decide what&#8217;s most important to you. If writing is one of those things, you will find time no matter how busy you are. If you don&#8217;t, writing isn&#8217;t important to you.</p>
