					<description><![CDATA[I never seem to be able to write as much as I want to. I have all these lofty goals of writing  thousands of words each day and in the end I sometimes write nothing. I wish I could be more productive and write more consistently. it&#039;s my dream to be a writer, so I really need to learn how to write more each day. I just don&#039;t have the focus and motivation to do it as much as I know I need to do it.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I never seem to be able to write as much as I want to. I have all these lofty goals of writing  thousands of words each day and in the end I sometimes write nothing. I wish I could be more productive and write more consistently. it&#8217;s my dream to be a writer, so I really need to learn how to write more each day. I just don&#8217;t have the focus and motivation to do it as much as I know I need to do it.</p>
